Comment 16: 
that's because gdb sees that function as "mra/Test-MultiplePackages/objects.
CreateUserFromParameters.  Some hairy quoting may be neccesary to convince gdb.  it may
be more convenient to set breakpoint by file:line.

work on a gdb commandline parser that understands the full Go syntax has been started,
but is not around the corner.
